The paper discusses a system for ranking answers to natural language questions, which involves processing both corpus and query using predictive annotation. This technique is commonly used in the fields of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
